Title: Resounding Repercussions
Description:
I did not mean for...

<Orweyna's eyes narrow.>

Fetch him, $n. You were exposed to the Black Blood, too. But Hannan took most of it.

He has entered the Unseeming, his mind shifted to a realm beyond our eyes through exposure to the Black Blood. You may need to join him, however far in he ventured, to retrieve him.

I will activate the nerubian cleansing instrument for when you return.

Do not lose yourself in that altered state.
ObjectivesText: Retrieve Hannan from the Abandoned Harvest Site inside the cave.
CompletionText: Is this real? Am I imagining the monsters?
RewardText: My head... It hurts. Everything feels so cloudy and... Help, please!

Objectives.Text: Follow Hannan into the Abandoned Harvest Site cave
